.png" alt="" /></h2></div></div></div><h1>3.&nbsp;<a href="http://tinyurl.com/bdd4e6s5" target="_blank">BetVictor</a></h1><div class="p"><p >BetVictor has recently improved its live betting features and has now solidified its position as one of the premier football betting offerings. They have a wide range of markets, including in-play Bet Builders and quick market bets are a unique feature. Their odds are less competitive than other major operators, but they make up for it, giving punters value back through many in-play odds boosts on a wide selection of games. They livestream less than competitors, and coverage isn't as broad as, but they offer a platform worth exploring for avid in-play football betting customers.</p><p ><strong>Get &pound;40 in free bets when&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://tinyurl.com/bdd4e6s5" target="_blank"><strong>sign up here to BetVictor</strong></a></strong>&nbsp;and bet just &pound;10!</strong></p><p ><img src="https://i.imgur.com/OBKetvW.png" alt="" /></p><h1>4.&nbsp;<a href="http://tinyurl.com/3aewupsy" target="_blank">Parimatch</a></h1><p >Parimatch is the same software and owner as BetVictor, so naturally it should rank alongside it's more established UK counterpart. If you're a fan of BetVictor then you'll enjoy Parimatch. It's worth boosting your live betting bankroll by claiming the &pound;40 welcome bonus below.</p><h2><div class="p"><div class="p"><div class="p"><div class="p"><strong><strong>A bonus bundle gets you &pound;40 in bonuses when you&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://tinyurl.com/3aewupsy" target="_blank">sign up here to Parimatch</a></strong></strong><strong>&nbsp;and bet &pound;10! A fantastic deal for punters this February!</strong></strong></div><div class="p"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/FOw39DR.png" alt="" /></div></div></div></div></h2></div><div class="p"><h1>5.&nbsp;<a href="http://tinyurl.com/SBBetfred40" target="_blank">Betfred</a></h1><p >Betfred have been a key operator in the UK market for many years and have 